Span.Text: Microsoft's Windows 10 Pro platform running on mobile devices allows industry specific applications and task-lead software to run exactly as it would on a desktop device.  Perform service specific tasks using dedicated apps running on a tablet device from anywhere at any time.

¬Microsoft’s cloud based Office 365 provides staff with a familiar suite of applications, supported by the scalability and flexibility of the cloud.  Applications work across any mobile device, enabling employees to access content at any time and from any location.  The Microsoft Lync collaboration platform also empowers staff to connect via voice, video call, desk-share and instant massaging, as well as conduct meetings, online.

Windows powered tablets and mobile devices allow staff to access documents and store notes wherever they, negating the need to travel back to a desk to record outcomes and pick up tasks. Travel costs are reduced and admin time is reduced, increasing productivity.

Remain operational when unforeseen circumstances such as flooding stops staff from being able to get into their place of work.  With the Microsoft Lync collaboration and Office 365 productivity apps, staff can relocate and continue to be productive from home or a different office location in minutes or hours, rather than days.

Microsoft mobility solutions allow more personalised interactions and the flexibility of completing activities at the most appropriate location for the customer.  Data is accessed and updated directly via a mobile device, avoiding trips to the office, with information that's fresh in the workers mind, so it's more accurate.  Microsoft's mobility solutions enable staff to see more people in less time and improve the speed of operations.
